airtrafficcontrol.app.deprecated

Class MainMenuMORREU

  • java.lang.Object
    • airtrafficcontrol.app.OptionsMenu
      • airtrafficcontrol.app.deprecated.MainMenuMORREU

  • public abstract class MainMenuMORREU
extends OptionsMenu
    Class that represents a Options Menu of this app and produces its string representation.

    Implementation notes

    As this menu is a unique and final piece not to be changed by other classes, there is no need to allow creation of instances of this class nor provide setter methods. The class itself represents the menu, all fields and methods are static.

    Author:
    Eva Gomes, Hugo Leal, Lucas Andrade
